# Privacy Policy for EightSparks Customer App

Effective Date: 14 Dec. 2024

## Introduction
Welcome to the **EightSparks Customer App**. At EightSparks, we prioritize the privacy and security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your data while using our app and services.

By using the EightSparks Customer App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

---

## Information We Collect
### 1. Personal Information
We may collect the following personal information when you use our app:
- Name
- Email address
- Phone number
- Delivery address
- Payment information (processed securely by third-party providers)

### 2. Non-Personal Information
We may also collect non-personal information, such as:
- Device information (e.g., model, operating system, unique device identifiers)
- App usage data (e.g., pages visited, actions performed)
- Location data (if location permissions are enabled)

---

## How We Use Your Information
We use the information collected for the following purposes:
- To process and deliver your food orders.
- To improve our app functionality and user experience.
- To provide customer support.
- To send you updates, promotions, and notifications (with your consent).
- To comply with legal requirements.

---

## Sharing Your Information
We do not sell your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your data in the following cases:
- **Service Providers**: With third-party vendors who help us operate the app and deliver services (e.g., payment processors, delivery partners).
- **Legal Compliance**: If required by law or in response to legal proceedings.

---

## Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. These measures include encryption, secure servers, and regular security assessments. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

---

## Your Choices
- **Account Information**: You can update or delete your account information within the app.
- **Location Data**: You can disable location access in your device settings.
- **Marketing Communications**: You can opt out of promotional messages by contacting us or using the unsubscribe link in emails.

---

## Children's Privacy
The EightSparks Customer App is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

---

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in this document, and you will be notified via the app or email if significant changes are made. Please review this policy periodically.

---

## Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
- **Email**: [info@eightsparks.com](mailto:info@eightsparks.com)
- **Website**: [https://eight-sparks.com/](https://eight-sparks.com/)

---

Thank you for trusting EightSparks to handle your food delivery needs!
